-- MSCI launches broad stock indexes excluding Russia
-- By Carolyn Cohn
-- Fri Aug 01, 2014 06:08AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Aug 1 (Reuters) - Index compiler MSCI said late on Thursday it was launching world and emerging market stock indices excluding Russia.

The indices were designed "for clients desiring to avoid exposure to Russian securities", MSCI said in a statement, following sanctions on Russia.